reviewText: My 2.5 year old- LOVE IT!  highly recommend.

My son loves this dvd. He is into farm animals and this is perfect because it shows all the different ones and also different characters from all his favorite baby tv shows! This keeps him happy and quiet in the car which is a lifesaver for me! I would definitely recommend this dvd to any parent!
Cute movie. Best part is it keeps my 6 month old grandson entertained when he is having his downtime before his nap.
my child loves watching the animals over and over.  she has learn from it.  I am going to buy more similar to it

It has great songs at a speed my LO enjoys. It is not so great for babys older than 3 years old two slow a pace.
I got this because I am an expat and baby Tv where I live is only in spanish. Wanna make sure baby learns proper English, so I figured all the TV  MUST and Will be in English. Plus you speak to the baby in English.....
Loved this video and so did my 2 year old, he doesn't seem to get enough of it!!! It's just a shame that this videos are so hard to find!!!
My daughter loves BabyTV, so this DVD was great for a road trip! It is hard to find BabyTV DVDs anywhere, so I appreciate the availability.
